        {
          "name": "Update Event",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "description": "Atualiza campos do evento. Campos permitidos dependem do status:\n- DRAFT: title, ticketPrice, registrationDeadline, paymentDeadline, venue, address, city, state, observations\n- OPEN: title, ticketPrice, registrationDeadline*, paymentDeadline*, venue, address, city, state, observations\n  * registrationDeadline e paymentDeadline só podem ser alterados por CIRCUIT_COORDINATOR (403 para outros)\n- CLOSED: observations\n- FINISHED: nenhum campo (422)\n\nCampos imutáveis (nunca editáveis): date, endDate, type, status, circuitId, createdById.",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Assembleia SP 2026 - Atualizada\",\n  \"registrationDeadline\": \"2026-08-01\"\n}"
            },
